headline: Thoma Bravo's Nearmap to buy insurance tech firm itel for over $1.3 billion
summary: Thoma Bravo-backed Nearmap has agreedto buy insurance technology provider itel from private equityfirm GTCR, the companies said on Tuesday, as it looks to expandits offerings across property...
